of text: geometric and annotation. Geometric text is implemented by stroke 
and area fonts that can be arbitrarily rotated and scaled before 
rendering. Annotation text is geometric text that has been transformed so 
that it always faces the screen. It is supported by a 
combination of a text routine listed below and the Screen Object 
described in  #!Lrendchp,dxall1129 h Rendering  #!EL  . #!N #!N #!I0 #!N #!N #!I0 #!N 
